    "version": "23.11.11",
    "description": "功能强大、符合人体工程学的 Windows 桌面组件系统，使用 Vue 构建。Desktop widgets for windows. built with vue3.",
    "homepage": "https://github.com/widget-js/widgets",
    "license": {
